abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Oklahoma defeats Hawaii, 84-81; other college basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: No. 3 Oklahoma remained unbeaten with an 84-81 victory over Hawaii in a Diamond Head Classic semifinal in Honolulu on Wednesday night.

headline.main: Oklahoma Holds Off Hawaii; Louisville Starts Hot in Rout
